<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1010430>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6 A – F. Notopentorchis javanica (Hübscher, 1937) from Hemiprocne longipennis (Rafinesque), Indonesia. A. Scolex. B. Anterior rostellar hook. C. Posterior rostellar hook. D. Mature proglottis, dorsal view. E. Genital ducts in mature proglottis, dorsal view. F. Gravid proglottis, dorsal view. Scale-bars: A, D, F, 100 µm; B, C, 20 µm; E, 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1010430/files/figure.svg" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

